# BackEnd API calls

- use the utils/api.ts function for invoking api calls

## To make API call use code as below in your component.
```ts
import { createApiClient } from "@/utils/api";
import { useAuth } from "@/hooks/useAuth";

const YourComponent = () => {
    const { token } = useAuth();
    const apiClient = createApiClient(token);
    const fetchData = async () => {
        const response = await apiClient.get<YourDataType>("/your-endpoint");
        // ... use response.data
    };
};
```
